{"tid":525774,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲周內第二宗！iPhone換電時爆炸","createTime":"2018-01-11T04:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T11:11:35.000Z","uid":107023,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc8a176124ec4e9fe88153f0d638b27c2aca2b7","tid":525774,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T04:11:38.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司為客戶提供減價換電之後，卻帶來電池著火的後遺症！繼瑞士蘇黎世蘋果店因電池著火而令七人受傷後，西班牙華倫西亞蘋果店內，亦在iPhone換電時發生電池爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙報章報道，意外發生在當地時間下午1時30分左右，店內人群需緊急疏散，消防員及警方均有接報，但蘋果員工為著火的電池舖上防火沙後，將火警撲熄，因此無需作出救援，亦未有人因此而受傷。"},{"pid":"ed908d905790c528141d8bf28730651b03001979","tid":525774,"uid":112416,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"證明換電真係好危險, 大家都係直接換新機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9540f3244b9d5875b90f7900fb49f4e61737d5a5","tid":525774,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T04:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f500705665c1e523c3f4836b1e563bb885c947","tid":525774,"uid":52068,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"我有一批價錢很好的電池，這是我的電話"},{"pid":"b0656a5e07a5f1b9f625bd4a63d6c1e326ee388f","tid":525774,"uid":23953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T05:08:59.000Z","msg":"用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f51c9c88663c20074f4c7d9814b282b582a7add","tid":525774,"uid":15835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"員工問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  出街換好危機，記得搵蘋果"},{"pid":"4171329e8f20df63bb3e0e4c780a57e6e3ef8260","tid":525774,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"到底點樣可以換到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\